description: Jessica is strong, tall and rugged. Growing up with three older brothers makes you tough. She is looking to kick the Ninja's ass. With an undefeated record, the Ninja is as worried as a windshield is of a fly. Can the Ninja be stopped? Is there a wrestler out there, anywhere that will take her on and beat her? My answer right now is no. Enjoy the Weekend Bonus update, from all at US.
title: Ninja (1-0) vs. Jessica (0-0)
